package.name: causal/sphinx
package.description: Installs a full-fledged Sphinx environment within your TYPO3 website. Builds and renders Sphinx/reStructuredText-based projects such as extension manuals, official reference guides or your own in-house documents as HTML/JSON/PDF either from TYPO3 Backend or from command-line, as you prefer. Features a reStructuredText editor with cross-reference browser and syntax highlighting.
